  ('dietitian-moex-00619', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關「糧食安全」之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["「糧食安全」包含了安全、足量、永續與經濟性等四個面向", "聯合國永續發展目標（SustainableDevelopmentGoals,SDGs）將消除飢餓，達成糧食安全作為 SDGs目標之一", "我國糧食安全指標「中度或重度」糧食不安全盛行率與「重度」糧食不安全盛行率均低於10%， 較大部分國家為佳", "性別平等教育也是達成糧食安全的重要因素之一"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6300cf2ce819", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cc22ae4e4f64", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0105", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00620', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '問卷調查時，下列那一種方法可確保得到的結果有代表性？', '["隨機分配", "隨機取樣", "方便取樣", "收集基本人口學資料"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6300cf2ce819", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cc22ae4e4f64", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0105", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00621', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某研究取得世界各國國民巧克力平均攝取克數，以及各國得到諾貝爾獎的獎牌數，並以此數據做 相關分析，結果發現兩者相關性很高。此研究最符合下列那一種研究設計？', '["生態研究（ecologicalstudy）", "橫斷研究（cross-sectionalstudy）", "營養調查（nutritionsurvey）", "世代研究（cohortstudy）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6300cf2ce819", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cc22ae4e4f64", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0105", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00622', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某研究使用在嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎（COVID-19）爆發前已蒐集的50萬人飲食與生活型態資料， 在COVID-19 大流行且疫苗尚未開始注射的期間，追蹤罹患COVID-19狀態與分析飲食習慣，比 起飲食品質較差者，飲食品質較佳者發生嚴重COVID-19的相對風險（Relative Risk）（95%信賴 區間）為0.59（0.47－0.74），下列敘述何者正確？', '["飲食和COVID-19嚴重程度無相關", "飲食與發生嚴重COVID-19之風險沒有統計顯著", "飲食品質較佳與發生嚴重COVID-19風險之降低有相關", "飲食品質較佳與發生嚴重COVID-19風險之提高有相關"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6300cf2ce819", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cc22ae4e4f64", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0105", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
